data.description: Escape to tranquility with this spacious property that offers peace and quiet on over 4+acres of land. With over 2200 sqft of living space, this residence is designed to provide ample room for comfortable living. The heart of the home features an extra-large family-activity room, perfect for gatherings and entertainment. The formal living room adds a touch of elegance, while the kitchen boasts a convenient breakfast bar for casual dining. One of the highlights of this property is the breathtaking views of the surrounding mountains, providing a picturesque backdrop to your everyday life. Plus a beautiful Arizona room to enjoy in every season. With endless possibilities, this property invites you to explore the potential it holds. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat, a spacious family home, or a versatile space for various activities, this property has it all. Don't miss the chance to make this heaven your own and enjoy the serenity of Arizona living.
